- Amiloride: ENaC block, no hormonal ADRs

🔹 **CAIs** (Acetazolamide): Metabolic acidosis, glaucoma, altitude sickness

🔹 **Osmotic** (Mannitol): Cerebral edema, acute glaucoma`,
