🔹 **Ezetimibe**: NPC1L1 block, ↓ absorption, add-on

🔹 **PCSK9i**: Monoclonal antibodies, ↓ LDL 50-60%

🔹 **Fibrates**: PPAR-α, ↓↓ TG, ↑ HDL\`,
